snippet.title: Star Wars: The Rise of Endgame
snippet.description:
I'm on to you Disney.

This video is meant to be a fun little video showing how Rise of Skywalker kind of copied Avengers Endgame. These scenes line SURPRISINGLY well.

The goal of this video is to show some blatant similarities between Star Wars: The Rise Skywalker and Avengers: Endgame. These take form with their being a version of the Portals scene and the I am Iron Man scene in The Rise of Skywalker. 

In the video, I combined parts of the final battles from the two movies, so instead of other superheroes, Lando and the Millennium Falcon show up to help Captain America. Instead of Rey replying to Palpatine after he says: "I am all the sith" you have Iron Man reply. 

Featuring footage from:
Lucasfilm's Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker (2019)
Marvel's Avengers: Endgame (2019)

For more Star Wars videos:
